<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ website_title | default('Ansible EC2 Deployment') }}</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 40px; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container { 
            background-color: white; 
            padding: 40px; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 { 
            color: #333; 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        .success { 
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            text-align: center; 
            font-size: 18px; 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info { 
            background-color: #e3f2fd; 
            padding: 20px; 
            border-left: 6px solid #2196F3; 
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .details { 
            margin-top: 15px; 
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        .details strong {
            color: #1976d2;
        }
        ul li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .timestamp {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><span class="emoji">ğŸš€</span>{{ website_title | default('Ansible Lab 10 Success!') }}</h1>
        
        <div class="success">
            <p>âœ… {{ deployment_message | default('EC2 instance deployed successfully with Ansible!') }}</p>
            <p>âœ… Nginx web server is running perfectly!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <h3><span class="emoji">ğŸ“‹</span>Server Information:</h3>
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Hostname:</strong> {{ ansible_hostname }}</p>
                <p><strong>Operating System:</strong> {{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</p>
                <p><strong>Architecture:</strong> {{ ansible_architecture }}</p>
                <p><strong>Private IP:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
                <p><strong>Public IP:</strong> {{ ansible_env.SSH_CLIENT.split()[0] if ansible_env.SSH_CLIENT is defined else 'Not Available' }}</p>
                <p><strong>CPU Cores:</strong> {{ ansible_processor_vcpus }}</p>
                <p><strong>Memory:</strong> {{ (ansible_memtotal_mb/1024) | round(1) }} GB</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <h3><span class="emoji">âš™ï¸</span>What was accomplished:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>ğŸ”’ Created AWS security group with proper firewall rules</li>
                <li>ğŸ–¥ï¸ Launched EC2 instance ({{ instance_type | default('t3.micro') }})</li>
                <li>ğŸ“¦ Installed and configured Nginx web server</li>
                <li>ğŸ¨ Deployed custom responsive web page</li>
                <li>ğŸ¤– Automated entire infrastructure deployment with Ansible</li>
                <li>âœ… Configured system security and updates</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <h3><span class="emoji">ğŸ”§</span>Technical Details:</h3>
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Kernel:</strong> {{ ansible_kernel }}</p>
                <p><strong>Python Version:</strong> {{ ansible_python_version }}</p>
                <p><strong>Uptime:</strong> {{ ansible_uptime_seconds | int | float / 3600 | round(2) }} hours</p>
                <p><strong>Ansible Managed:</strong> âœ… Yes</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timestamp">
            <p>ğŸ•’ Deployed on: {{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</p>
            <p>Generated by Ansible automation</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>